                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18131027-87-victim909 t18131027-87-viclabel516"></join>. The handkerchiefs were pinned to a pile of flannels at the door, inside of the door. I went to the door; I saw the prisoner about four yards from the door, with the handkerchiefs in his possession; I pursued him. He dropped the handkerchiefs; a man picked them up, and gave them to me. These are the handkerchiefs; they are my master's property.</p>
